Did you know?
23 million girls in India drop out of school every year when they start menstruating.

It’s time to change that.

I'm on a mission to empower underprivileged girls by ensuring access to:

Free sanitary pads

Menstrual health & mental well-being workshops

Sustainable livelihood opportunities for marginalized women

Education is a right, not a privilege.
Let’s help these girls reclaim their future—one pad at a time.

Join my mission. Spread the word. Donate if you can.
Together, we can keep girls in school.

— 
Karuna Chandirani 
Mrs India Universe
Mrs North Bengal 2018

#PadsForFreedom #MenstrualEquity #GirlsEducation #BreakTheTaboo #EndPeriodPoverty #DonateForChange #EmpowerHer #PragyaFoundation #Knushii #PeriodPositive #VoiceForChange

latestPosts.caption:
The moment you've all been waiting for!
As we celebrate the 10th glorious year of the I-Glam Championship 2025, it's time to unveil our prestigious jury panel – the icons who represent Beauty with Responsibility.

Let’s welcome Karuna Chandirani, a woman of grace, wisdom, and unstoppable ambition, as one of our respected jury members. A true queen who has touched lives with her elegance and purpose, her journey stands as a beacon of inspiration for many.

"Elegance is when your strength speaks softly, and your presence empowers others." – Karuna Chandirani

Get ready to witness Bengal’s finest talents shine on stage, evaluated by names known and celebrated across the fashion and glamour industry.

You won’t want to miss this!
Let’s connect and celebrate the essence of style, purpose, and excellence.
